VERY LOW ELECTRIC BILLS - Solar powered home PAID FOR - You will love this modern and sleek remodeled four bedroom home in Citrus Springs! It features a split floor plan with the Master bedroom on one side and the additional three bedrooms, main bath and laundry on the other side. It has a brand-new kitchen with new high-end appliances, fixtures and fans with LED lighting. Freshly painted inside and out, there's nothing to do here but move in!!  It has a smart doorbell and thermostat system that you can control from your phone. The closets have been decked out with new organizational systems, maximizing space along with keeping your items neat and easily accessible. There are new 2-inch wooden blinds on all windows. Spacious backyard with no rear neighbor and a patio for your cookouts. It is located on a quiet street with only one neighboring home to the side. New roof with solar panels 2022! Citrus Springs is a deeded community but has no HOA fees. It features the famous Withlacoochee State Trail for biking, hiking and great nature walks, local library, community center for social events, lighted tennis courts and a park for the kids. The golf course includes a restaurant, putting greens and driving range for hours of fun. It is conveniently located just minutes from boating, fishing, diving, beautiful freshwater springs, restaurants, shopping, medical services, supermarkets and more and let’s not forget the excellent school system.
